    <summary>Specifies the CICP (Coding-Independent Code Points) transfer function for a color space.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

CICP transfer functions are defined in ITU-T H.273 / ISO 23091-2 and describe the gamma curve applied to linear light values. Used with <xref:M:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp*>.
]]></format></remarks>
